query:
SELECT s.id as supplierId, s.companyName, u.id as userId, u.email 
FROM suppliers s, users u 
WHERE s.id IN (SELECT id FROM suppliers LIMIT 10) 
AND u.email = '12@supplier.com'
LIMIT 1
